# Each version is a markdown file named <version>.md in this folder.
# Schema lives in src/content/config.ts. Frontmatter required:
#
#   ---
#   version: '1.7.0'            # string, required
#   date: 2026-05-10            # ISO date, required
#   summary: 'One-liner...'     # required, shown in collapsed state
#   bump: minor                 # optional: major | minor | patch
#   ---
#
# Body is normal markdown. The page at src/pages/changelog.astro renders
# every entry newest-first as collapsible <details> blocks; the latest is
# open by default.
#
# Important: do NOT add a README.md to this folder — Astro's content
# collection globs every .md and validates it against the schema, so a
# README without version/date frontmatter will break the build. Put
# explainer notes in MIGRATION.md or a .gitkeep / .txt instead.
#
# v1.x versions still to port (drop one .md file per version):
#   1.6.0  Word export + print pagination
#   1.5.0  Cyber Essentials integration
#   1.4.0  Tabletop Exercise mode
#   1.3.0  DfE Cyber Security Hub integration
#   1.2.0  Prioritised Action Plan tab
#   1.1.11 → 1.1.0  post-launch fixes line
#   1.0.0  initial public release
#
# Source: the <div class="card"> blocks inside <section id="tab-changelog">
# in the legacy v1.x index.html.
